100,‌000 Stocks.‌ 30 Years of History.‌ One Platform.‌  ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ 

https://tikr.acemlna.com/lt.php?x=4lZy~GDMKqXL7s3Azw-7gulv13FSuQAkw-kvXnjHJ3fOD5_7-ky.0OJt3HVzidTvk_Y1bHPEJnaaT8DvyNxIUOBzPbKRia 

**For investors who want every edge in their research**

Go from 3 years of U.S. data to 

**30 years of global coverage**, with the deepest toolkit we've ever
built

Dear TIKR user,

Back in March, we launched a new tier of service at TIKR called Ultimate. It was designed as our most comprehensive level of access, built for serious investors who wanted the deepest data, the broadest screening, and a fully customizable research workspace.

We 

**closed** Ultimate to new subscribers in late March to make sure our charter members got the experience they signed up for before we expanded access. Three months in, their feedback has shaped the product in real ways, and it speaks for itself:

* 

**"I just upgraded to Ultimate and have to say, I really do enjoy it. I went through the dashboard tutorial and it's powerful."**

* 

**"I recently upgraded to Ultimate. I love the product, especially the ability to look back 30 years."**

* 

**"This is amazing and will save me so much time. I've been running about 80 processes a week surfacing similar catalysts - so I'm thrilled about this."**

That encouraging feedback, combined with
continued requests from subscribers who missed the original window, is why we're reopening Ultimate today.

**Starting today, for a brief window only, we're extending the same pricing structure our charter members received in March.**

Here is what that means for you:

* A 20% discount on the upgrade cost (the prorated amount for the remainder of your current Plus term), 

****and**** 20% off your first renewal.

* A 14-day money-back guarantee. If Ultimate is not the right fit, we will return your subscription to Plus and restore your existing pricing.

Log In and Access Your TIKR Ultimate Invitation! https://tikr.acemlna.com/lt.php?x=4lZy~GDMKqXL7s3Azw-7gulv13FSuQAkw-kvXnjHJ3fOD5_7-ky.0OJt3HVzidTvk_Y1bHPEJnabT8DvyNxIUOBzPbKRia

Here's what Ultimate unlocks beyond your current free access:

* 

**Coverage expands from roughly 15,000 U.S. stocks to 100,000+ globally**: Many of the best fundamental opportunities sit across global markets where fewer analysts are looking and
mispricings persist longer.

* 

**Financial history jumps from 3 years to 30 years:** Instead of a snapshot, you can study how businesses performed through the early '90s recession, the dot-com bubble, the 2008 financial crisis, and COVID.

* 

**Analyst estimates extend from 1 year to 5 years forward:**See further into what the market expects, and identify where your own analysis diverges from consensus. That divergence is where investment returns come from.

* 

**Transcript access goes from 90 days to 15 years, with search, audio, and slides:** Search any keyword across a decade and a half of earnings calls, listen to the actual call audio, and review the presentation slides. You can hear the conviction in a CEO's voice during a tough Q&A, not only read the words.

* 

**Unlock Excel export, segmented financials, management guidance, and beats/misses tracking**: These are the tools that turn surface-level analysis into institutional-quality research. Break down revenue
by segment, export clean data into your own models, track guidance accuracy, and see how the market reacts to earnings surprises quarter by quarter.

* 

**Custom Dashboard with 300+ column options**: Replace the standard 25-column watchlist with a fully personalized command center. Unlimited stocks, unlimited views, and total control over the data you see.

* 

**Catalyst Tracker**: An entirely new workflow. Screen for corporate actions across 120+ event categories, including M&A activity, activist involvement, spin-offs, guidance changes, and red flags. Find companies undergoing transformative events before the market fully prices them in.

* 

**100+ new screening factors**: Go beyond the standard screener with factors like P/NCAV, Altman Z-Score, FCF ex-SBC per Share, 10-Year Average ROIC, PEG ratio, and implied multi-year future valuations.

And while Ultimate has been closed to new subscribers, we have not been sitting still. Charter member feedback has shaped what we
have shipped over the past three months. A few of the most meaningful additions:

* 

**Estimates Revisions**: See how Wall Street consensus is moving on the names you follow, and how quickly sentiment is shifting, before it shows up in price.

* 

**Portfolio Tracking**: Monitor your holdings directly inside the same workspace where you do your research, so your portfolio sits alongside the financials, models, and transcripts you are already working with.

If you spent any time looking at Ultimate in March, the product you would log into today is meaningfully deeper than the one we first launched.

****Backed by a 14-day money-back guarantee!****

If Ultimate isn't the right fit, we'll refund your payment in full and your account simply returns to your free plan. We're confident you'll feel the difference, but we want you to experience it for yourself with zero risk.

We built Ultimate for investors like you: serious, long-term focused, and always looking for an edge in
the quality of your research process. We think you'll feel the difference immediately.

Log In and Access Your TIKR Ultimate Invitation! https://tikr.acemlna.com/lt.php?x=4lZy~GDMKqXL7s3Azw-7gulv13FSuQAkw-kvXnjHJ3fOD5_7-ky.0OJt3HVzidTvk_Y1bHPEJnabT8DvyNxIUOBzPbKRia

Best regards,

David Hanson
TIKR

P.S. The 20% discount on your first year and the 20% off your first renewal are only available through June 30 at 5 PM ET. After that, the window closes. If you've been considering a serious upgrade to your research toolkit, this is the best price you'll see. Log in to learn more! https://tikr.acemlna.com/lt.php?x=4lZy~GDMKqXL7s3Azw-7gulv13FSuQAkw-kvXnjHJ3fOD5_7-ky.0OJt3HVzidTvk_Y1bHPEJnabT8DvyNxIUOBzPbKRia

